Supply Chain Security (20%)</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Monitoring, Log=
ging and Runtime Security (20%)</strong></p><p><br></p></li></ul><p>Every q=
uestion is written to feel like the real exam, helping you spot gaps in you=
r knowledge and build confidence.</p><p><br></p><p>This set of exercises is=
